{"sectionId":787,"sectionIdLiteral":"787","humanId":"final-lessons","volumeId":"workbook","locale":"en","titleInfo":{"title":"This holy instant would I give to You.  Be You in charge. For I would follow You,  certain that Your direction gives me peace.","ownlineNumber":"Lessons 361 to 365"},"annotation":"W-361-365","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"acim-text final-lessons\"> <div data-paragraph-id=\"787#1\"><p class=\"p-normal\"><span class=\"pnr\">1.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"787#1:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>And if I need a word to help me, He will give it to me.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"787#1:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>If I need a thought, that will He also give.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"787#1:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>And if I need but stillness and a tranquil, open mind, these are the gifts I will receive of Him.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"787#1:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>He is in charge by my request.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"787#1:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>And He will hear and answer me, because He speaks for God my Father and His holy Son.</span></p></div> </div>","firstWords":"And if I need a word to help me, He will give it to me. If I need a thought, that will He also give. And if I need but stillness and a tranquil, open mind, these are the gifts I will receive of Him.","contentType":"acim-content","seoTitle":"Lessons 361 to 365: This holy instant would I‚Ä¶ | ACIM","seoDescription":"‚ú® A Course in Miracles with üéß Audio! Read and listen to ‚ÄúLessons 361 to 365: This holy instant would I give to You. Be You in charge. For I would follow You, certain that Your direction gives me peace‚Äù from the Workbook. ‚Ä¶","desktopBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Final Lessons","lead